  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this observational study is to obtain multi-center data on HeartMate II (HMII)
      patients managed with reduced anticoagulation or anti-platelet regimes, and the incidence of
      thrombotic and bleeding adverse events associated with these regimes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
